Package: ReichbR
Title: SMC Tools for Krankenhaus Erreichbarkeitsanalysen
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
	person("Simon", "Essink", email="simon.essink@sciencemediacenter.de", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1390-3885"))
Description: Provides helpers for accessing the SMC hospital driving time database and for running
    Erreichbarkeitsanalysen. The package bundles utilities to load and transform the source
    data, to filter spatial selections, and to export summaries for downstream reporting.
